oads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.o51git9aot2l-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.o51git9aot2l-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.o51git9aot2l-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://twitter.com/nijisanji_app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nijisanji</a>的小分队“ <a href="https://www.valz-official.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VΔLZ</a> ”和<a href="https://x.com/SideM_official" target="_blank" rel="noopener">THE IDOLM@STER SideM</a>的小分队“DRAMATIC STARS”合作演唱会“VΔLZ×DRAMATIC STARS COLLABORATION LIVE 〜戏剧演部〜”将于7月21日（星期日）18:00开始直播。</p><p>整个合作现场将在 ASOBI STAGE 上直播，部分免费部分将在 YouTube 上直播。</p><p> <a href="https://idolmaster-official.jp/live_event/valz_ds_gekitekienbu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处</a>购买送货票。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000939.000030865.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd. 新闻稿</a></p><h2>Live2D官方应用程序“nizima LIVE”×TV动画“Buiden”合作纪念材料分发</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.3599r3ebp2ty-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.3599r3ebp2ty-1024x538.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.3599r3ebp2ty-1024x538.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.3599r3ebp2ty-300x158.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.3599r3ebp2ty-768x403.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.3599r3ebp2ty-jpg.webp 1200w" width="1024" height="538" /></a></p><p>为了纪念Live2D官方的VTuber脸部追踪应用程序“ <a href="https://nizimalive.com/" target="_b